  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，描述工业IoT场景下文件通知的发送流程。核心是从ActuatorController检测到待上传文件开始，经过MQTT Broker，最终到达EdgeNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我理解为ActuatorController作为起点，当存在待上传文件时进入WAITING_FILE状态。那SENDING状态是由WAITING_FILE直接转移过去的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "SENDING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，WAITING_FILE到SENDING是自动流转的。但SENDING状态有个特殊触发条件——当MQTT Broker检测到没有文件时也会进入SENDING。这是为了处理Broker端的空轮询情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "SENDING",
        "No file"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了从MQTT Broker到SENDING的转移，标注为\"No file\"。接下来SENDING之后应该是创建发送实体对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SENDING",
        "REGISTERED",
        "Creata entità su SEND"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，REGISTERED之后分两条路径：正常情况是文件上传完成后到UPLOADED再到COMPLETE；但如果一开始就没有文件需要上传，直接从REGISTERED跳到COMPLETE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "REGISTERED",
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE",
        "No file da caricare"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "清楚了，这是条件分支。那COMPLETE之后呢？最终状态是ACCEPTED吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "ACCEPTED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，COMPLETE到ACCEPTED，标注说明这个ACCEPTED状态同时适用于SEND操作。最后ACCEPTED指向EdgeNode，表示流程结束，通知到达边缘节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
